{"word":"τηρέω","slug":"τηρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>τηρέω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘maintain in a secure state’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on personal interest or obligation <b>keep <a href='B:480 7:9'>Mk 7:9</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:500 2:10'>J 2:10</a>; <a href='B:500 17:11'>17:11f</a>; <a href='B:530 7:37'>1 Cor 7:37</a>; <a href='B:540 11:9'>2 Cor 11:9</a>; <a href='B:560 4:3'>Eph 4:3</a>; <a href='B:610 5:22'>1 Ti 5:22</a>; <a href='B:620 4:7'>2 Ti 4:7</a>; <a href='B:670 1:4'>1 Pt 1:4</a>; <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 1</a>, <a href='B:720 6:1'>6</a>; have on hand <a href='B:500 12:7'>J 12:7</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on penal aspect, <b>watch <a href='B:470 27:36'>Mt 27:36</a>, <a href='B:470 27:54'>54</a>; put/keep under guard <a href='B:510 12:5'>Ac 12:5</a>; <a href='B:510 16:23'>16:23</a>; <a href='B:510 24:23'>24:23</a>; <a href='B:680 2:4'>2 Pt 2:4</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘be in compliance’, of response to instruction <b>keep, observe <a href='B:470 19:17'>Mt 19:17</a>; <a href='B:470 28:20'>28:20</a>; <a href='B:500 8:51'>J 8:51f</a>, 55</b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in J; <b><a href='B:510 15:5'>Ac 15:5</a>; <a href='B:660 2:10'>Js 2:10</a>; <a href='B:690 2:3'>1 J 2:3</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in 1 J; <b><a href='B:730 1:3'>Rv 1:3</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Rv. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:τηλικοῦτος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:τήρησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}